title: Former in-laws charged with murder after model's legs found in fridge
description: The former in-laws of a model whose legs were found in a fridge have been charged with her murder.

title: Israel and Palestinians agree to de-escalate tensions and 'prevent more violence' ahead of holy month
description: Israel and the Palestinians have agreed to de-escalate tensions and "prevent more violence".

title: At least 30 migrants drown after boat breaks apart off Italy
description: At least 30 migrants have reportedly drowned after their boat broke up off the southern coast of Italy's mainland.
